'''Scipione del Ferro''' (6 brayeṛ 1465 - 5 nuwambir 1526), ikka-t-inn iga yan umusnak awṭalyan, d umusnak akkʷ izwuren s tɣarast nna s da iferru yan tagda "cubic".

==Tudert-nnes==
Ilul-d Scipione del Ferro g Bulunya, agafa n Ṭṭalyan, iga memmi-s n Floriano d Filippa Ferro. Baba-s Floriano, iswuri yad g temguri n walkaɣiṭ, iger amguran nna mi tettuɣul tilit-nnes ɣer usnulfu n tsiggezt g temrawant n yid 1450, ayedda yujjan Scipione ad yili asadef s mennawt twuriwin seg mayd imeẓẓi. Iwwel yat tmeṭṭut yaru id-s yat terbat nna mi iga s yisem Filippa, ɣef yemma-s nettat.

Irwas is d taɣiwant n Bulunya ad d-ikka, mani g ittyasay amm yan iggaren tiɣuriwin g "Arithmetic" akked "Geometry" aseggʷas n1496. Iseggʷasen-nnes ineggura, izzri-ten da iswuri g yiger n umseɣsenzi.

==Azuzzer n twuri-nnes==
Meqqar d yan warra seg dar del Ferro ur inejjim. Da tetturruy tamentilt-ad s umata-nnes ɣer tagʷit-nnes i umsawaḍ ɣef twuriwin-nnes. G udɣar n ad d-ifser tiwengimin-nnes, da tent-immal ɣas i yat tufrint imeẓẓin g yimeddukkal d yinelmaden-nnes.

Tella turda n mas d-ikka uya tamyurt illan dar yimusnaken n tizi-ann g t-nn-kkan da tteggan "challenges" gratsen mnid n umata. kudenna idegga yan umusnak s "challenge" n wayya, da ittili ɣef ku yan gi-sen ad ifru tamukrist n wayyaḍ. G kigan n tikkal, da itterzu "Perdant" n "challenge" g usidrem (financement) neɣ d ansa-nnes ammas n tɣiwant. Ikka-t-nn Del Ferro da ittiksaḍ ad "être challenge" d irwas is d imk-ann a'ɣef yujja twuri-nnes akkʷ ixatren tga tuffirt afad ad si-s isten iɣef-nnes kudenna nn-yufa agayyu-nnes g tuẓẓumt n kra n "challenge".
